<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA77">
<l>vēṅkaṭamum viṇṇakarum veḵkāvu maḵkāta</l>
<l>pūṅkiṭaṅki ṉīḷkōvaṟ poṉṉakaru – nāṉkiṭattu</l>
<l>niṉṟā ṉiruntāṉ kiṭantā ṉaṭantāṉē</l>
<l>yeṉṟāṟ keṭumā miṭar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘Vēṅkaṭam, the heavenly city<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">I.e., Vaikuntam.</note>, Veḵkā and the large golden city</l>
<l>of Kōval, with a moat of unwithering flowers, in [those] four places</l>
<l>he stood, he sat, he lay, he walked;’</l>
<l>when one says so, affliction gets destroyed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
